---
title: Mumbai-Spiced Beef & Bacon Pie with Cheesy Veggie Mash Topping & Pear Salad
description: Potato topped pie is a weeknight dish we wait in anticipation for. Contain your excitement because this one has cauliflower mashed into the topping and baked on richly spiced beef and bacon filling. We know you’ll love when the topping is pulled apart and the Cheddar cheese stretches with it.
